                     </decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d2">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#8r #15v #24v #35v #44r #50v #60v #73r #82r #88v #103r #114v #117v #124r #130v #144r #151v" facs="010 018 027 038 046 053 063 075 084 091 105 117 120 126 133 146 154">fols. 8r, 15v, 24v, 35v, 44r, 50v, 60v, 73r, 82r, 88v, 103r, 114v, 117v, 124r, 130v, 144r, 151v</locus> (line of alternating red and black dots)
                    </decoNote>
